Symbol.Script_3D:
! Horizontal Expansion Tank
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1
endRed2 = endRed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN endRed2 = 0
HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2+endRed2, -dTDepth/2, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2+endRed2, dTDepth/2, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2-endRed2, -dTDepth/2, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2-endRed2, dTDepth/2, legHeight+dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2+endRed2, 0, legHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2-endRed2, 0, legHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2+endRed2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2-endRed2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- TANK --- !
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 AND ConStatus_1 THEN GROUP "cylind" ADD -dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 ROTy 90 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, endRed, 1+2+32, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_1/2, 360, 4001 DEL 2 ENDGROUP ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN GROUP "tank" ADD -dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 CALL "MEP_m_Tank" PARAMETERS tankLen = dTWidth, tankDia = dTDepth, endRed = endRed, ringOn = 0, typ = 2, tankPos = 0, tankMat = MainBoxMaterial, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, res = res DEL 1 ENDGROUP ELSE ADD -dTWidth/2, 0, legHeight+dTDepth/2 ROTy 90 CYLIND dTWidth, dTDepth/2 DEL 2 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN result_1=ADDGROUP("cylind","tank") PLACEGROUP result_1
KILLGROUP "cylind" KILLGROUP "tank" ENDIF
! --- SUPPORT --- !
ADDx -dTWidth/2+endRed+0.15 ROTz 90 CALL "MEP_m_Tank_support_4" PARAMETERS supLen = 0.10, supHeight = legHeight+dTDepth/4, supThick = 0.02, footWidth = dTDepth+0.06*dd, footThick = 0.025, tankDia = dTDepth, tankDeepening = dTDepth/4, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, supMat = MainBoxMaterial, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, res = res, hptsID = 100 DEL 2
ADDx dTWidth/2-endRed-0.15 ROTz -90 CALL "MEP_m_Tank_support_4" PARAMETERS supLen = 0.10, supHeight = legHeight+dTDepth/4, supThick = 0.02, footWidth = dTDepth+0.06*dd, footThick = 0.025, tankDia = dTDepth, tankDeepening = dTDepth/4, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, supMat = MainBoxMaterial, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, res = res, hptsID = 200 DEL 2
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConEdgeVisible_1 = 0 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Horizontal Expansion Tank
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2+endRed, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2+endRed, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2-endRed, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2-endRed, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- Tank --- !
rr = (dTDepth/2)/SIN(180-2*ATN((dTDepth/2)/endRed)) PUT dTWidth/2-endRed, -dTDepth/2, 1, dTWidth/2-rr, 0, 901, dTWidth/2-endRed, dTDepth/2, 3001, -dTWidth/2+endRed, dTDepth/2, 1, -dTWidth/2+rr, 0, 901, -dTWidth/2+endRed, -dTDepth/2, 3001
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
LINE2 dTWidth/2-endRed, -dTDepth/2, dTWidth/2-endRed, dTDepth/2 LINE2 -dTWidth/2+endRed, -dTDepth/2, -dTWidth/2+endRed, dTDepth/2
! --- SUPPORT --- !
ADD2 -dTWidth/2+endRed+0.15, 0 ROT2 90 CALL "MEP_m_Tank_support_4" PARAMETERS supLen = 0.10, supHeight = legHeight+dTDepth/4, supThick = 0.02, footWidth = dTDepth+0.06*dd, footThick = 0.025, tankDia = dTDepth, tankDeepening = dTDepth/4, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, supMat = MainBoxMaterial, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_pen = gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen = gs_back_pen, gs_fill_type = gs_fill_type, hptsID = 100 DEL 2
ADD2 dTWidth/2-endRed-0.15, 0 ROT2 -90 CALL "MEP_m_Tank_support_4" PARAMETERS supLen = 0.10, supHeight = legHeight+dTDepth/4, supThick = 0.02, footWidth = dTDepth+0.06*dd, footThick = 0.025, tankDia = dTDepth, tankDeepening = dTDepth/4, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, supMat = MainBoxMaterial, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_pen = gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen = gs_back_pen, gs_fill_type = gs_fill_type, hptsID = 200 DEL 2
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
IF ConStatus_1 THEN ! --- 1st CONNECTION --- ! PUT ConPosX_1, 0, 1, 0, 1, 801, ConPosX_1+(rr-SQR(rr^2-(ConWidth_1/2)^2)), ConPosY_1+ConWidth_1/2, 1001, ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1+ConWidth_1/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT ConPosX_1, 0, 1, 0, -1, 801, ConPosX_1+(rr-SQR(rr^2-(ConWidth_1/2)^2)), ConPosY_1-ConWidth_1/2, 1001, ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1-ConWidth_1/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConEdgeVisible_1 = 0 DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Horizontal Expansion Tank
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
!!IF dTWidth < 1.00 THEN !! dTWidth = 1.00 !! dTDepth = 0.33 !!ENDIF !!IF dTDepth < 0.33 THEN dTDepth = 0.33 !!IF dTDepth > (dTWidth-0.60)*1.5 THEN dTDepth = (dTWidth-0.60)*1.5 dd = dTDepth/0.46 endRed = dTDepth/3
z = 0
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z
Symbol.Script_UI:
! Horizontal Expansion Tank
UI_DIALOG `Специальные Параметры MEP`
DIM ui_vis_attr[4][4] FOR i = 1 TO 4 FOR j = 1 TO 4 ui_vis_attr[i][j] = 0 NEXT j NEXT i ui_vis_attr[1][1] = 2 ui_vis_attr[1][2] = 1 ui_vis_attr[1][3] = 7
ui_vis_attr[2][1] = 1 ui_vis_attr[2][2] = 237 ui_vis_attr[2][3] = 68 ui_vis_attr[2][4] = 14
DIM ui_con_type[1] ui_con_type[1] = 0
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS ALL ui_vis_attr = ui_vis_attr, ui_centerline_vars = 0, ui_con_type = ui_con_type, ui_system_var_pos = 2, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
Symbol.Script_VL:
! Horizontal Expansion Tank
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 0 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
! --- MAIN PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN !! IF dTWidth < 1.00 THEN !! dTWidth = 1.00 !! dTDepth = 0.33 !! ENDIF !! VALUES "dTWidth" RANGE [1.00, ] !! IF dTDepth < 0.33 THEN dTDepth = 0.33 !! IF dTDepth > (dTWidth-0.60)*1.5 THEN dTDepth = (dTWidth-0.60)*1.5 !! VALUES "dTDepth" RANGE [0.33, (dTWidth-0.60)*1.5] !! IF legHeight < 0.10 THEN legHeight = 0.10 !! VALUES "legHeight" RANGE [0.10, ]
IF dTWidth < 1.00 THEN dTWidth = 1.00 dTDepth = 0.33 ENDIF VALUES "dTWidth" RANGE [1.00, ] IF dTDepth < 0.33 THEN dTDepth = 0.33 PARAMETERS dTDepth=dTDepth ENDIF IF dTDepth > (dTWidth-0.60)*1.5 THEN dTDepth = (dTWidth-0.60)*1.5 PARAMETERS dTDepth=dTDepth ENDIF VALUES "dTDepth" RANGE [0.33, (dTWidth-0.60)*1.5] IF legHeight < 0.10 THEN legHeight = 0.10 VALUES "legHeight" RANGE [0.10, ] ENDIF
PARAMETERS A = dTWidth PARAMETERS B = dTDepth+0.06*(dTDepth/0.46) PARAMETERS ZZYZX = dTDepth+legHeight LOCK "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
PARAMETERS MEP_NumberConnections = 1
! --- 1st CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 1 ConName = `Труба Впускного Соединения `
ConDVecX = -1 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 0
ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = -1 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE (0, dTDepth/4] PARAMETERS ConDepth_1 = ConWidth_1 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_1" VALUES "ConLength_1" RANGE [0, ]
PARAMETERS ConPosX_1 = -dTWidth/2 PARAMETERS ConPosY_1 = 0 PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1 = legHeight+dTDepth/2 ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF setProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
